WEBVTT

00:00:07.854 --> 00:00:14.854 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Ev’ry newborn child,
Ev’ry drop of rain,

00:00:14.854 --> 00:00:21.645 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Ev’ry golden ray of sun,
Each head of grain—

00:00:21.645 --> 00:00:28.937 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
All are gifts from God;
They reveal his way.

00:00:28.937 --> 00:00:35.854 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Miracles performed by him
sustain us each day.

00:00:35.854 --> 00:00:43.104 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So, what are we to do
with a gift so rare

00:00:43.104 --> 00:00:50.104 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But to love the One who gave it
and show him we care.

00:00:50.104 --> 00:00:57.604 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
No matter what we do,
We never can earn it.

00:00:57.604 --> 00:01:08.687 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This gift is still a gift—
The miracle of life.

00:01:12.604 --> 00:01:19.395 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Others may give up,
Lose their will to try,

00:01:19.395 --> 00:01:26.812 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Echoing the wife of Job:
“Curse God and die.”

00:01:26.812 --> 00:01:33.937 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We are not that way;
Praise to God we give,

00:01:33.937 --> 00:01:40.812 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Thanking him for ev’ry
precious moment we live.

00:01:40.812 --> 00:01:47.812 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So, what are we to do
with a gift so rare

00:01:47.812 --> 00:01:55.145 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But to love the ones around us
and show them we care.

00:01:55.145 --> 00:02:02.479 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
No matter what we do,
We never can earn it.

00:02:02.479 --> 00:02:13.312 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This gift is still a gift—
The miracle of life.

